PayrollCycleSepolia
├── given contracts are deployed on Sepolia
│   ├── it should have MockUSDC at expected address
│   ├── it should have ConfidentialUSDC at expected address
│   └── it should have ConfidentialPayroll at expected address
├── given employer mints and wraps USDC
│   ├── when employer mints MockUSDC
│   │   └── it should credit employer balance
│   ├── when employer approves cUSDC
│   │   └── it should set allowance
│   └── when employer wraps USDC to payroll
│       ├── it should emit USDCWrapped
│       └── it should credit payroll cUSDC balance
├── given employer registers employee with encrypted salary
│   ├── when salary is encrypted client-side via relayer SDK
│   │   └── it should produce externalEuint64 handle + inputProof
│   ├── when batchAddEmployees is called
│   │   ├── it should emit EmployeeAdded
│   │   └── it should increment employeeCount
│   └── when getSalary is called by employer
│       └── it should return decryptable salary matching original
├── given employer runs payroll
│   ├── when runPayroll is called
│   │   ├── it should emit PayrollExecuted
│   │   └── it should update lastPaidAt
│   └── when employee checks cUSDC balance
│       └── it should equal the salary amount
├── given employee decrypts own salary
│   ├── when employee calls getSalary
│   │   └── it should return handle with transient ACL
│   └── when handle is decrypted via relayer
│       └── it should match the registered salary
└── given unauthorized caller
    └── when outsider calls getSalary
        └── it should revert with Unauthorized
